545
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,420
 na tom individualizmu lako nastane

546
00:33:14,420 --> 00:33:17,100
 i kapitalizam i sve ono što danas nama dolazi.

547
00:33:17,320 --> 00:33:19,120
 E sad mora da s time spojimo.

548
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:20,220
 Ovo ste krasno rekli,

549
00:33:20,220 --> 00:33:21,300
 da je poganski element,

550
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:23,380
 to logično malo zvuči peorativno

551
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:26,040
